column5: Wife and I got invited for supper yesterday by PJ,Jason and his brother Jared.Boys made a great meal and had great conversations about everything.Got to love the flag.
We had a wonderful time meeting Ms. Sylvia and getting to know her. You ..not so much .LOL. We really enjoyed the evening with both of you. Hopefully more to come in the future. PjShorthorn
Hmmmm, that flag looks oddly familiar. We had a similar one on the top of our houseboat on Lac Seul this past July. Could it be the same culprit? I hope y'all had a great time on Eagle Lake!
